WOLE BALOGUN, Ado Ekiti Governor of Ekiti State, John Kayode Fayemi has lost a commissioner in his administration, Mrs Biola Adeosun. Adeosun was before her demise, the state Commissioner in the Local Govt Service Commission. She was also the women leader of the John Kayode Fayemi (JKF) Movement, and former Secretary, Ido-Osi Local Government Area of the state. A statement by Suleiman O. Nasiru, who is Secretary of JKF Movement, described late Adesoun as a staunch loyalist and ally of the JKF family. READ ALSO:Â When your DPO is a woman!